'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #2005] on 22 April 2000 at 7:12:58 pm'!"Change Set:		1039SemaphoreCmp-smaDate:			22 April 2000Author:			Stefan Matthias AustDiscussing a problem with comparing Semaphores, Wim Boot and Tim Rowledge agreed upon>	I think Semaphore comparison (including #hash) should be identity based,>	not content based.So I implemented (but not really tested) it that way."!!Semaphore methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'sma 4/22/2000 18:48'!= anObject	^ self == anObject! !!Semaphore methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'sma 4/22/2000 18:48'!hash	^ self identityHash! !